---
title: Open Sloppy Joes with Simple Slaw
description: We’ve made it easy for you to recreate this all-American family favourite in just six simple steps. These hearty open sandwiches are made by piling high ground tomato bbq beef mince inside a grilled ciabatta bun, topped with crunchy lettuce and cheese. Fun and delicious but as the name suggests things can get a little messy - so make sure you have lots of napkins!
